        "text": "EUGENE, July 5. -(AP)- A Eugene railroad cashier said Friday he saw\nsilvered disks being dropped out of a light airplane flying over this city.\nF. R. Smith, Rt. 2, Eugene, an assistant cashier for the Southern Pacific"
